{"tid":1500140,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港鐵總部大樓投訴 違反處理意外事故指引","createTime":"2019-08-24T03:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T01:28:31.000Z","uid":186,"like":99,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"60f86c8d7cecc2b8d0dd41e4e9a2a2e71f01d35b","tid":1500140,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:10:33.000Z","msg":"指引寫明港鐵要點處理意外事故，公然違反處理意外事故指引<br />\n<br />\n處理意外事故指引<br />\n如發生意外事故，員工須要跟據以下指引，儘快控制情況：<br />\n-在整個意外事故中保持鎮定<br />\n（緊張的員工只會令情況更壞，相反，保持鎮定和有自信的員工懂得處理混亂情況及安撫受驚的乘客。）<br />\n-有條理地思考及按正確步驟控制情況<br />\n-報告負責人或事發地方之業主有關事故情況及給予協助<br />\n-發生意外事故時，無可避免會引致恐慌，儘量安撫乘客及告知情況已受控制<br />\n-防止群眾圍觀<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">-儘快指引群眾去到安全地方<br />\n-協助列車服務儘快回復正常，減低對乘客造成不便</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://aes.mtr.com.hk/Content/images/MTR.AES/HTMLContent/WEB_REFERENCE_MATERIALS/bbb9d308-d9c4-4d95-a0dd-193dd5730428/fdc12022-030b-47fb-b500-dcfee62624c4.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faes.mtr.com.hk%2FContent%2Fimages%2FMTR.AES%2FHTMLContent%2FWEB_REFERENCE_MATERIALS%2Fbbb9d308-d9c4-4d95-a0dd-193dd5730428%2Ffdc12022-030b-47fb-b500-dcfee62624c4.pdf&d=LRWPp57H9HH2b7ruXTkGLjyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=26c2ab47\" target=\"_blank\">https://aes.mtr.com.hk/Content/images/MTR.AES/HTMLContent/WEB_REFERENCE_MATERIALS/bbb9d308-d9c4-4d95-a0dd-193dd5730428/fdc12022-030b-47fb-b500-dcfee62624c4.pdf</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P6kCgEB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP6kCgEB.png&h=72586e90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7621405ed66ccfa37f30b17119dbc715b0f61bca","tid":1500140,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86b5d2edfa409f08e5937a5d861437ff30112529","tid":1500140,"uid":48436,"l